## DkStd_Std bootstrap handoff

This repository now pins the latest MlFront release tarball and starts the
real Dk0 packaging split:

- `DkStd_Std.Dk0.Bundle@2.4.2.173` tracks the upstream source tarball
- `DkStd_Std.Dk0.DuneCache@2.4.2` repackages that tarball into a cacheable zip
  for all supported slots
- `DkStd_Std.Dk0@2.4.2` emits `bin/dk0.exe` only for Windows x86_64; the other
  executable slots remain out of scope until the toolchain is broadened

The current bootstrap path is intentionally explicit so the executable slice can
be widened later without changing the public package layout again.
